$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,cl.The security in this place is way over the top.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.Brad, stay back. If things get rough, do what you can to help us keep Buddie away from the gun.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.Hey! This is mine! Get away from me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.Hey! Get your hands off me! I can’t see!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.What the hell is going on here? What are you doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.It’s over Buddie. You killed Father Parker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.What’s wrong with you? I didn’t do nothing!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.Give us your access card for the security room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.You’re making a mistake Steedly. I didn’t kill anyone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.Father Parker is downstairs with a bullet in his chest because of your itchy trigger finger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.We’re calling the police. Now give us the access card!");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,cl.The security room doesn’t use a card. It operates on a handprint. So unless you’re going to hacksaw Parker’s hand off his cold dead body you’re going to need me to open the door.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,ex.So maybe stop pointing that gun my way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.Fine. We’re going to walk to the door nice and slow.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.We wait until sunrise and then everyone leaves. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.We don’t want a panic, do we Brad?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,fr,ex.Can we keep this a secret? Just between us, okay?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.Denny, go to the chapel foyer and make sure no one enters the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,cl.As soon as the water level drops I want every last one of those ESU people off my property.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,ba,op.How about now? Is that the last thing you needed?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,an,op.Hey! None of your business! Leave me alone!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.Don’t you even think about breaking him out. He’ll kill us all!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,ma,op.No he wont! You’re just mad that you’re not in charge. That’s why you locked him up!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.That’s what he told you? That we’re jealous of his authority?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,cl.Only you would believe that you idiot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,sa,ex.Thank you for helping us Brad. Please don’t tell anyone about Buddie or Father Parker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.I’ll help you out this time Mendel. But eventually I’m going to spill the beans.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,op.Just wait until you leave. I can’t deal with any more right now.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.You better stay out of trouble or I’ll tell your Mom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.What the hell dude! Get off him!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,wo,op.Buddie! Denny’s been eaten by the Dame Woods Demon!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.Simon here says that you have security footage from outside the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ma,op.I can’t believe a nun stole my Serum. She has no idea what it even it! How rude!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,fr,ex.I found another one of those coins.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,cl.Let me guess... you lost it again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,fr,op.Not this time. I still got it and I’m keeping it!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.God damn it Simon! Just give it to me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,an,ex.I’ll give it to you if you do something for me first.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.Fine. What do you want? Something to eat I assume.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,ba,ex.No! I want you to convince my Mom to let me go with Buddie into the woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Why do you think I’d be able to convince her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,an,cl.Because she trusts you for some reason.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.Okay. I’ll do it. And then you have to give me the gold coin.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,fr,op.Are you going to ask my Mom if I can go with Buddie on the hike?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.Sure Simon. I’ll see what I can do. But you’ll owe me your gold coin.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,wo,op.What did my Mom say? Can I go on the hike?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.I’m working on it Simon. Don’t rush me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,an,cl.Why did you wake us up so early? ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,op.What’s wrong Buddie? Why did you call us all in here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,ex.Somebody in this room shot Father Parker and it wasn’t me and it wasn’t Tillman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,an,cl.What are you talking about? How do you know anything?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.I manage to get the security footage from that evening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.Father Parker went into the chapel shortly after Simon and Brad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ba,ex.Yes. He came in to complain about our meeting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,ex.After the power went out, everyone left except Parker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,ex.And now apparently he got up and left the Chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.One of you ESU people shot him!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,ma,op.That’s insane! Why would we give two shits about your stupid priest?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.I don’t know what you’re scheming here...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.But Brad has sure spent a lot of time visiting the chapel since he got here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.You’ve been quite the snoop Brad. And I think it’s clear that you’re up to something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.Woah dude! I didn’t even want to be here!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.I want you to come with me Brad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,ma,op.What are you doing! Don’t point that gun at him!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,ba,ex.You’re failing to include your private investigator. He was there as well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.Hey! Keep your hand off of VaIerie!!!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.What’s going on Valerie? What are you planning?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,ma,op.This is insane! Give me one good reason we would shoot a priest!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,op.Brad, did you say the priest dude is still alive?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.That’s impossible. I saw him myself. He was dead. I’m sure of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.You’re coming with me Brad. We can’t have you endangering any other lives.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.I’m not dangerous! Get your hands off me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu.ma,op.Tillman and I are going to get help. When I get back, we’ll let the authorities deal with this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.Until then, Brad is getting locked up. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.And I suggest you East State people better stop snooping around unless you all want locked up too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,ma,ex.You’ve got no proof! Mendel stop him!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.I don’t trust you people. If Parker was shot in the chapel then it must have been one of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,ma,op.Who says it can’t be you Mendel?! Or your private investigator, who just so happened to run off without us yesterday!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,ma,ex.Yeah! I think the PI did it! And ran away!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.Shut up! I don’t want to hear any more. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,sa,op.We don’t know it was them. It could be any of us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.Brad here is the only one who kept snooping around the chapel. And I caught him trying to hide the body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.I know enough to warrant keeping him locked up until we get back! Now stay out of my way!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.It’s nothing, I just need to talk to Andy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,ba,ex.I think I saw him on the first floor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.You said that Tillman is cleaning up his mess. What mess? Mendel doesn’t appear to know anything about the Serum. So why go after him?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,an,cl.I can’t tell you anything. I’m already in enough trouble as it is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,an,ex.Do you want me to keep making Serum?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.I don’t get it. People’s lives are in danger. You have to tell me why!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.What do you mean? He wanted us to drink the Serum?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.The diagram you gave me earlier... Parker was using our Serum but we aren’t involved with Parker. He discovered our Serum on his own.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.But you said Tillman wanted everyone to be under its effects. He didn’t help Parker build his basement dungeon?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,an,cl.No! Tillman’s plan was much bigger than Parker’s. Parker was just an opportunist.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.So Tillman came here to make us all drink Serum? That doesn’t make any sense. Why do that? Did he want to bone the girls too?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ma,ex.No idiot! Not us! He didn’t come here to drug us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Then who did he want to drink the Serum?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,an,ex.We’re all under the effects of the Serum.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Who’s under the effects of the Serum?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.What exactly did you and Tillman do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sh,op.You contaminated the town’s water with Serum!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,fr,cl.Yeah. It seemed like a good idea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.Serum is surprisingly cheap to produce. We just made a ton of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.So... Tillman killed Denny because he knew what you two were doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,sa,ex.Well... Uh... Denny didn’t know yet, but Tillman didn’t want to take any chances.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,sa,cl.I told him not to do it. I was watching Denny closely. It was my job to make sure he didn’t find out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,cl.But Tillman was too scared having someone snooping around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Why did he make you do it? Why have you be the guy with the gun? ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,cl.It was supposed to look like Mendel did it. But believe me Brad. I didn’t want to do it!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Well now I know about it too. Is he going to kill me now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,ex.I don’t know what he’s going to do. I think it’s in everyone’s best interest to get to Tillman before he gets to us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.It’s going to have to be up to us. Mendel and Buddie aren’t going after Tillman anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.Mendel is instead searching for a cell signal to call and have a helicopter pick us up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,op.No! They need to handle Tillman first!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.I don’t know. Finding a cell signal seems like a reasonable plan to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,op.You still want to save the day don’t you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Well... I did help to get the cell phone number for the helicopter guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,fr,ex.Let’s kill Tillman. He doesn’t suspect me and he doesn’t know I told you anything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Maybe you’re right. But why hasn’t Tillman already barged in here looking to kill us? He’s staying in the woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.He’s expecting Buddie and Mendel to come back for him. He knows the only way out is through him. He’s waiting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.He might be waiting forever because I don’t even know which direction Buddie and Mendel went.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.Once night falls he’ll come back. He’s not prepared to spend the night out there. Is he?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,op.I suppose you’re right. If Buddie and Mendel haven’t crossed paths with him he’ll probably try attacking here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,wo,op.What’s going on? Did you really shoot the priest?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,ex.Simon. Don’t freak out. Andy is going to help us find Tillman and put an end to this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,an,op.I’m going to tell my Mom you got out!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.You two are going to trap Tillman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,op.Us? What are you going to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.I spoke with Father Parker in the woods and he told me that he is coming tonight to kidnap one of the girls.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.Why would Father Parker tell you his plan?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Uhh... I forced it out of him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,fr,ex.Look at it this way... I wasn’t trying to murder a priest, I was saving the women from him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.Good god Andy! Stop talking about killing people. While you two capture Tillman I am going to capture Father Parker. Then we’ll let the cops sort it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.Ok. I have a plan. Meet me in the Dame Woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,fl,ex.Yeah! She looked like she wanted it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.You wouldn’t think of it as cheating on you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,fr.op.If it’s Va1erie... I think I could let that one slide.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,fl,ex.I’d like to hear the juicy details of that encounter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,op.Amber came running by. She looked upset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Oh shit! I better not go in there. Mendel will kill me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,ex.Give me one good reason I shouldn’t lock you up right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Woah! Mendel. I know we’ve had our differences, but I’ve got something I need to tell you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.Well... Uh... I spoke with him out in the woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.I tried to tell him to stop his killing spree, but he told me that he still needed to get to you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,cl.What possible reason would he have to shoot me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,cl.I don’t know, but without Buddie’s gun you’re a sitting duck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.Thanks for the good news Brad. Are you finished?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.Buddie knows where he dropped his gun. Maybe you should go get it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,op.What are you doing back? Did you find Tillman?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.He was looking for the gun? That’s not what he told us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,cl.What do you think he told me? What do you know about him?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,ex.Andy told us that Tillman wants to kill Buddie and myself. He says this is some sort of cleanup job.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sh,ex.Good god! This is why you need to find Tillman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.Don’t tell me what to do! You realize that once this is all over I’m going to use this to bury you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.You people are insane! Tell me why Tillman is after us!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,ex.Don’t tell me to calm down! There’s a madman trying to kill me! Your madman is trying to kill me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,op.Mendel please. This doesn’t have to escalate.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.You’re done Valerie. Your whole school is finished once all this gets out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.Stop it Mendel! I have something to tell you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.I saw Father Parker in the woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.You better watch your tone Mendel. You think you’ve got dirt on us? You have no idea what I have on you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,wo,op.So it’s true! Parker has risen from the dead!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,cl.You’re just as fucked as we are.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.He won’t talk. Whatever Tillman is up to, Andy was working with him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,an,cl.Whatever you uncover I assure you we have nothing to do with it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.Come with me Brad. We need to talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Don’t worry Val. I have a plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,an,ex.Don’t you dare lay a finger on Bradley.");
